    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0777b16"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>黃州<anchor xml:id="beg0777sgsz5"/>九井<anchor xml:id="end0777sgsz5"/><persName key="A010534">玄策</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0777c13"/><persName key="A010534">釋玄策</persName>，俗姓魯，<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>人也。幼隨父商估，赴<lb
ed="T" n="0777c14"/><placeName key="PL000000014411">天台山</placeName>光明會，乃隋朝<persName key="A001301">智顗禪師</persName>立教，年別<lb
ed="T" n="0777c15"/>九月。遠近州邑黑白二眾鳩聚。<persName key="A010534">策</persName>覩殊異，遂<lb
ed="T" n="0777c16"/><anchor xml:id="beg0777sgsz6"/>于<anchor xml:id="end0777sgsz6"/><placeName key="PL000000014691">禪林寺</placeName><persName key="A010536">智廣師</persName>下出家。遊方見<persName key="A003623">江西大<lb
ed="T" n="0777c17"/>寂</persName>，頓開翳障。及遍參問，覩黃陂<placeName key="PL000000026508">九井山</placeName>奇<lb
ed="T" n="0777c18"/>秀，乃結茅為舍，學侶若蟬之走明也。或慰<lb
ed="T" n="0777c19"/><persName key="A010534">策</persName>曰：「<persName key="A010534">師</persName>之耐寂<anchor xml:id="beg0777004"/>寞<anchor xml:id="end0777004"/>如此乎？」<persName key="A010534">策</persName>曰：「致道者<lb
ed="T" n="0777c20"/>忘心矣，<persName key="A010534">吾</persName>樂甚哉。」以<date from-iso="+0854-02-05" key="j20330132033367" to-iso="+0855-01-25"><name>大中</name>八年</date>現疾而滅。<lb
ed="T" n="0777c21"/>續勅諡大師曰<persName key="A010534">圓寂</persName>，塔名智覺焉。</p>
